Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_time_unit(25.10)                                timing_time_unit(25.10)

Name
       timing_time_unit

Syntax
       timing_time_unit <string>

       Default: none

       Specifies the timing units to be used for timing constraints and timing
       reports.  The default units for timing are inferred from the timing li-
       braries. You can override this  inference  by  explicitly  setting  the
       value to none, 1ns, 1ps, 10ps, or 100ps .

       Setting  this  variable  explicitly is the same as executing the setLi-
       braryUnit -time command to set time units.

       To set this global variable, you can use the set command.

